                    Well, I-I've
                never noticed   

08:54.000 --> 08:55.067
any bolts                       
in that floor.                  

08:55.135 --> 08:56.535
You know, come                  
to think of it,                 

08:56.636 --> 08:58.404
                Bird, Parish,   
                    Auerbach,   

08:58.505 --> 09:00.205
nobody knows how many bolts     
are in that floor, huh?         

